          <td class="px-4 py-3">No</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3">Allocation ledger &mdash; lives outside the repo</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p class="text-muted mb-8">
    Once you commit <code class="text-accent-light">.treeline.yml</code> and <code class="text-accent-light">AGENTS.md</code>, every teammate who installs <code class="text-accent-light">gtl</code> can run <code class="text-accent-light">gtl new &lt;branch&gt; --start</code> and get a fully isolated environment. See <a href="/use-cases/onboarding/" class="text-accent-light hover:text-accent underline underline-offset-2">New developer, one command</a> for that walkthrough.
  </p>

